All Classes

  • All Classes Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    GraphicsEngine
    The basic Graphics engine, for drawing things on a webcam stream using Imgproc
    JoystickControl
    This program has basic driving control of the robot, it also includes a very basic instance of FtcDashboard, this is used primarily for viewing the camera remotely so we can see what the robot is doing remotely.
    LiveViewPipeline
    A pipeline that creates a basic crosshair on the screen, this is used to see what the robot sees.
    LoggingEngine
    The basic Logging Engine, for logging things to a MultiTelemetry object
    Skystone
    This program is used as an example of the Skystone detection algorithm.
    SkystonePipeline
    Pipeline to detect the color yellow and categorize / mask it
    SkystonePipeline.Location
    Locations of the Skystones, output from SkystonePipeline
